{
  "name": "Earth Release Rising Rock Technique",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Earth.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You tear two large chunks of stones from the ground using the strength of your chakra alone, hurling them at a single target. Make two ranged ninjutsu attacks against the target dealing 2d8 Earth damage on a hit.</p><p>The two large chunks of stone remain after being hurled, being counted as an Quake Shard, occupying two spaces of your choice within 5 feet of the original target.</p><p>Select two spaces within 5 feet of you when you cast this jutsu. These two spaces from which you pulled the stones from count as difficult terrain until cleared, which takes at least 10 minutes of work.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. When this jutsu is cast at B-Rank, increase the number of attacks by +1. When this jutsu is cast at S-Rank, increase the number of attacks by +1.</p>",
